{
  "title": "AD #10 · Attracting People to Rural Areas (Path C · Design)",
  "lessons": [
    {
      "translation": "Claire 想补贴农民，Kelly 想引入商店和餐厅。",
      "phrases": ["Claire wants", "farm subsidies", "and Kelly wants", "to bring in shops", "and restaurants."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "两种想法都只治了乡村衰退的表面。",
      "phrases": ["Both ideas", "treat the surface", "of rural decline."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "真正的解法是政府先在乡村建起强公共服务——好学校、诊所、快速网络——让私人生活在上面生长。",
      "phrases": ["The real fix", "is for the government", "to set up", "strong public services", "in rural areas first —", "good schools,", "clinics,", "and fast internet —", "and let private life", "grow on top of that."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "逻辑在于顺序。",
      "phrases": ["The logic is about order."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "补贴农民只会吸引那些本来就想务农的人。",
      "phrases": ["Subsidizing farmers", "only attracts people", "who already want to farm."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "引入商店需要村庄还不存在的顾客基础。",
      "phrases": ["Bringing in shops", "needs a customer base", "that the village", "does not yet have."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "两者都陷入同一个陷阱：服务弱的地方人不会搬去，人少的地方服务也不会出现。",
      "phrases": ["Both run into", "the same trap:", "people will not move", "where services are weak,", "and services do not appear", "where people are few."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "公共服务能打破这个循环，因为政府可以不等市场就开始建。",
      "phrases": ["Public services break this loop,", "because a government can build them", "without waiting for the market."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "一旦一个村子有了好学校、可靠诊所、快速网络，新类型的居民就成为可能——远程工作者、退休者、厌倦城市成本的年轻家庭。",
      "phrases": ["Once a village has", "a good school,", "a reliable clinic,", "and fast internet,", "a new kind of resident", "becomes possible —", "remote workers,", "retirees,", "and young families", "tired of city costs."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "美国的塔尔萨把一万美元的补贴和更好的光纤结合，三年里吸引了三千多名专业人士。",
      "phrases": ["Tulsa in the United States", "paired a $10,000 grant", "with better fiber optics", "and drew more than three thousand professionals", "in three years."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "几个空心化的西班牙小镇以同样的方式重获生机。",
      "phrases": ["Several empty Spanish towns", "came back to life", "the same way."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "先把底建好。只要有留下来的理由，商店、工作甚至农场都会跟上。",
      "phrases": ["Build the base first.", "Shops, jobs, and even farms", "will follow", "once there is a reason", "to live there."]
    }
  ]
}
